  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3977960/extras/95ddf701b6ea13177d838b22c6a02eb9.avif?t=1774180462\" width=1280 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revive the golden era of 90s arcade shooters with crisp high-res graphics, unlocked 60+ FPS smoothness, and relentless bullet-hell action. Battle waves of alien invading forces in a thrilling single-player campaign or grab a friend for intense online co-op multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic 90s shmup gameplay with modern polish </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-resolution graphics and buttery-smooth 60+ FPS</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single-player campaign packed with frenetic action!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online co-op for 2 players—team up and survive! </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DeSci-themed achievements by real scientists!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a dystopian future dominated by machines!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exclusive soundtrack by Italian rock band \"KHA!\"</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free-to-play—jump in anytime! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of the only starfighter engineered with infected alien technology, absorb the glowing bio-virus to fuel your weapons, and save a dystopian Earth from technorganic invaders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Tips and How to Play:</u></i></strong> the glowing enemies will give you power-ups and restore your shield and ammo. Blast through the enemies and use them to feed the ship and keep it in power-up mode. If you kill the power-up enemies, you'll get a score penalty</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3977960/extras/4c04bc5d594badba9adbcd50fd669044.avif?t=1774180462\" width=1560 height=878 /></span> </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3977960/extras/95ddf701b6ea13177d838b22c6a02eb9.avif?t=1774180462\" width=1280 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revive the golden era of 90s arcade shooters with crisp high-res graphics, unlocked 60+ FPS smoothness, and relentless bullet-hell action. Battle waves of alien invading forces in a thrilling single-player campaign or grab a friend for intense online co-op multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic 90s shmup gameplay with modern polish </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-resolution graphics and buttery-smooth 60+ FPS</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single-player campaign packed with frenetic action!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online co-op for 2 players—team up and survive! </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DeSci-themed achievements by real scientists!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a dystopian future dominated by machines!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exclusive soundtrack by Italian rock band \"KHA!\"</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free-to-play—jump in anytime! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of the only starfighter engineered with infected alien technology, absorb the glowing bio-virus to fuel your weapons, and save a dystopian Earth from technorganic invaders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Tips and How to Play:</u></i></strong> the glowing enemies will give you power-ups and restore your shield and ammo. Blast through the enemies and use them to feed the ship and keep it in power-up mode. If you kill the power-up enemies, you'll get a score penalty</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3977960/extras/4c04bc5d594badba9adbcd50fd669044.avif?t=1774180462\" width=1560 height=878 /></span> </p>",
